    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for precise torque vectoring. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains tight, featuring a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup that provides exceptional feedback and cornering poise. While the body shows light cosmetic wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in peak operational form.",
