    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and long-term care. Finished in a classic deep metallic, the exterior retains a high-gloss luster, though a discerning eye will find minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with standard highway use. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the premium upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all digital displays and climate controls function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent synthetic oil change and comprehensive brake inspection performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. We have the full service history available for review. If you are looking for a reliable, aesthetically pleasing vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for the road, this is an excellent choice.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
