      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to a high standard of mechanical and aesthetic integrity. It offers a refined driving experience, characterized by a responsive powertrain and a well-appointed interior that remains in commendable condition. Every aspect of this vehicle reflects a commitment to quality and consistent care, making it an ideal choice for the professional seeking both performance and reliability. We invite you to experience the superior craftsmanship and enduring value of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
