    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-loved and looked after over the years. It\u2019s the perfect blend of reliable and stylish, ready to hit the road for its next big adventure! If you're looking for a solid car that\u2019s been treated right, you\u2019re going to love this one. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
