      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing for a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS solenoid overhaul to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration that offers precise turn-in and high lateral stability. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive, making this an ideal candidate for a driver-centric collection.",
